query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser') AND t1.name IN ('certificate',
'django-templates',
'frameworks',
'gruntjs',
'installer',
'match',
'office365',
'react-router',
'sas',
'timeout',
'webgl')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10 group by t1.name;
